Mereu18

Preamble

library(scran)
library(scater)
library(patchwork)
library(ExperimentHub)

Load data

# load SCE from EH
eh <- ExperimentHub()
q <- query(eh, "Kang18_8vs8")
sce <- eh[[q$ah_id]]

Wrangling

# keep controls only
sce <- sce[, sce$stim == "ctrl"]
# drop unassigned cells & multiplets
sce <- sce[, !is.na(sce$cell)]
sce <- sce[, sce$multiplets == "singlet"]
# sparsify counts
counts(sce) <- as(counts(sce), "dgCMatrix")
# standardize metadata
colData(sce) <- DataFrame(
  cluster = sce$cell,
  batch = factor(sce$ind))
# tabulate cell counts
table(sce$cluster, sce$batch)
                   
                     101  107 1015 1016 1039 1244 1256 1488
  B cells            107   44  453  126   27  116  216  218
  CD14+ Monocytes    202  209  779  369  126  415  390  295
  CD4 T cells        293  158  848  422  189 1068 1001 1182
  CD8 T cells         74   20  179  536   26   58  131   58
  Dendritic cells     21    8   30   19    9   47   26   43
  FCGR3A+ Monocytes   80   32  252  115   34   56   69  101
  Megakaryocytes      11    6   20    8   31   14   14   18
  NK cells            70   40  177  128   19  105  261  116
sce <- logNormCounts(sce)
tbl <- modelGeneVar(sce, block = sce$batch)
hvg <- rowData(sce)$hvg <- tbl$bio > 0
sce <- runPCA(sce, subset_row = hvg)
thm <- list(
  theme(aspect.ratio = 1, legend.key.size = unit(0.5, "lines")),
  guides(col = guide_legend(override.aes = list(alpha = 1, size = 2))))
plotReducedDim(sce, "PCA", colour_by = "batch", point_size = 0.1) +
plotReducedDim(sce, "PCA", colour_by = "cluster", point_size = 0.1) +
plot_layout() & thm

Appendix

saveRDS(sce, "outs/Kang18.rds")
